22 passengers abducted in Pasni
QUETTA â€“ Unidentified armed men abducted 22 passengers in Kandasool near Pasni area of Balochistan on Wednesday.
According to Levies sources, a Gwadar-bound passenger coach carrying commuters from Karachi was on its way when some armed motorcyclists intercepted the coach.
They took away at least 22 commuters at gunpoint to unidentified destination. Levies force has cordoned off the entire area and started efforts for their recovery.